subject: example message with attachments
seed_key: TZSZQBfvmuz


Attach Files to the Message
===================

List added files under `attachments` frontmatter section.Images are automatically compressed. Control the sizewith `media_constraints` frontmatter section.


Inline Attachments
------

Inline attachments are placed into message body,when linked like so:🔗 cat<../internal/media/testdata/cat.jpg> (Cat Photo by Cindy vanHeerden).


Creative Commons Credits
----------------


- **cat.jpg:** Cindy vanHeerden.
- **panda.jpg:** Snow Chang.
- **camillion.jpg:** Regan Dsouza.



